## AccountID

Type: `string`

Type: `string`

Type: `string`

## DeviceRegistrationID

Type: `string`

Device registration ID.

## Hostname

Type: `string`

The device hostname.

## SerialNumber

Type: `string`

The device serial number.

## Timestamp

Type: `int or string`

## Toggled

Type: `bool`
